  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nFor security reasons, it would be good to run Nethermind as **non-root by default**\r\nTo bring  some context, Erigon runs using a non-root user from a long time ago https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/blob/v2021.07.04/Dockerfile#L20\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nCreate a user in the Dockerfile and make it the default one\r\n",
