    "body": "We're going to introduce a [chiseled](https://ubuntu.com/engage/chiselled-ubuntu-images-for-containers) and rootless Docker image very soon. That will be a separate image to avoid breaking existing setups that depend on root access. \r\n\r\nWe're currently testing that, so it will likely be published in one of the upcoming releases.\r\n",
